    return(
        <form action="/autenticate" method="POST">
            <fieldset>
                <label for="email">E-mail</label>
                <input 
                    id="email" 
                    name="email" 
                    type="email" 
                    inputmode="email" 
                    autocomplete="username"
                />
            </fieldset>
            
            <fieldset>
                <label for="password">Senha</label>
                <input 
                    id="password" 
                    name="password" 
                    type="password" 
                    autocomplete="currrent-password"
                />
            </fieldset>
            <button type="submit">Entrar</button>
        </form>
    )
};
